Revision history for Perl extension Text::Bind.

0.04  Wed Jul 07 1999
	- Fixed bug checking for filehandle bindings.  Strings with
	  "GLOB" in them would be mistaken as filehandles.

0.03  Sat Apr 24 1999
	- fixed some -w warnings

0.02  Tue Mar 30 1999
	- add support data site loops
	- an array can be bound to a data site

0.01  Thu Jan 27 1998
	- initial bundled release
